{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaQueryList","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/matches\"><code>matches</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/media\"><code>media</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/addListener\"><code>addListener()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/removeListener\"><code>removeListener()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/change_event\"><code>change</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>這是一個實驗中的功能</strong><br>此功能在某些瀏覽器尚在開發中，請參考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">兼容表格</a>以得到不同瀏覽器用的前輟。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><code>MediaQueryList</code> 物件維護一組針對 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a> 的 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\">media querie</a> , 並且當 media querie 相對應的文件狀態改變時，觸發註冊的事件處理器通知之。</p>\n\n<p>MediaQueryList 物件讓我們不用一直定期去偵測，而是直接去觀察文件的狀態變化。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"method_overview","title":"Method overview","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>void <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList#addlistener()\">addListener</a>(MediaQueryListListener listener);</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>void <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList#removelistener()\">removeListener</a>(MediaQueryListListener listener);</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td class=\"header\">Property</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Type</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Description</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>matches</code></td>\n   <td><code>boolean</code></td>\n   <td><code>true</code> 當 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a> 目前狀態符合 media query list 所維護的條件; 否則 false。 唯獨<strong>。</strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>media</code></td>\n   <td><code>DOMString</code></td>\n   <td>序列化 (serialized) 的 media query list.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"addlistener()","title":"addListener()","isH3":true,"content":"<p>添加一個新的事件處理器 (listener)，若 listener 已存在則無作用。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">void addListener(\n  MediaQueryListListener listener\n);</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"parameter_(for_addlistener_method)\">Parameter (for addListener method)</h4>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"listener\"><code>listener</code></dt>\n <dd>當 media query 對應的狀態改變時所觸發的事件處理函數 (<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryListListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>)。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"removelistener()","title":"removeListener()","isH3":true,"content":"<p>移除一個事件處理器 (listener)，若 listener 不存在則無作用。</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">void removeListener(\n  MediaQueryListListener listener\n);</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"parameter_(for_removelistener_method)\">Parameter (for removeListener method)</h4>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"listener_2\"><code>listener</code></dt>\n <dd>欲移除的事件處理函數 (<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryListListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>)。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaQueryList","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":" ","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification_2","title":"規範標準","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/csswg/cssom-view/#the-mediaquerylist-interface\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">The CSSOM View Module: The MediaQueryList Interface</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"延伸閱讀","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\">Media queries</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries\">Using media queries from code</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\"><code>window.matchMedia()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryListListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Method overview","id":"method_overview"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":" ","id":"specification"},{"text":"規範標準","id":"specification_2"},{"text":"延伸閱讀","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"MediaQueryList 物件維護一組針對 document 的 media querie , 並且當 media querie 相對應的文件狀態改變時，觸發註冊的事件處理器通知之。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaQueryList","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MediaQueryList","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"MediaQueryList","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MediaQueryList","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/mediaquerylist","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/mediaquerylist/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList","title":"MediaQueryList"}],"pageTitle":"MediaQueryList - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}